<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4272395>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 34. Helochares (Helochares) pallens (MacLeay, 1825), chaetotaxy of head capsule, dorsal view. A – median part of head capsule, second instar. B–D – third instar larva: B – median part of head capsule; C – intraspecific variation of secondary sensilla between PA6 and PA7; D – intraspecific variation of secondary sensilla on outer part of antennal socket. Secondary sensilla are marked by a black rhombus." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4272395/files/figure.png" .

